Attack on Titan: Eren's Determination Theme Screenshot
======================================================

This is a placeholder image. To add a real screenshot:

1. Activate the "Attack on Titan: Eren's Determination" theme
2. Open a code file showcasing the theme's colors
3. Take a screenshot
4. Save it as attack-on-titan.png in this folder
5. Replace this file

Theme Features:
